# Fix MIME type for .mjs and .wasm - prevents "application/octet-stream" error on Netlify
# See: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/78807249/expected-a-javascript-module-script-but-the-server-responded-with-a-mime-type-of

/*.mjs
  Content-Type: application/javascript

/*.wasm
  Content-Type: application/wasm

/assets/*.mjs
  Content-Type: application/javascript

/assets/*.wasm
  Content-Type: application/wasm
